{"tid":1936211,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"飯敍中招 美一家四死兩危","createTime":"2020-03-21T05:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T06:19:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f20c003a6438fb3e99443adcd9213f6b376e2dc3","tid":1936211,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200321/4ENK72PVZEMXCWDSRMNTPLPOVA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200321%2F4ENK72PVZEMXCWDSRMNTPLPOVA%2F&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=502409a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200321%2F4ENK72PVZEMXCWDSRMNTPLPOVA%2F&h=cde00cc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200321/4ENK72PVZEMXCWDSRMNTPLPOVA/</a><br />\n<br />\n飯敍中招 美一家四死兩危<br />\n<br />\n美國新澤西州一個大家庭月初共晉晚餐後，四名家庭成員，包括年紀最大的73歲母親相繼患上武漢肺炎死亡，另外兩名成員確診感染後情況嚴重、一人確診後狀況較為穩定；有親人形容：「這對整個家庭來說是一場無法承受的悲劇。」<br />\n<br />\n73歲的富斯科（Grace Fusco）擁有11名子女與27名孫兒，她確診武漢肺炎後，周三晚上不治離世。她辭世時仍不知道，她的五旬女兒麗塔，五天前已經因為染上同一病毒不治，她的兒子卡爾米內數句鐘前亦因此病逝，另一兒子文森特前天也死於武漢肺炎。現時，兩名情況嚴重的家庭成員要依賴維生系統，另一人穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200321/large/1584722812_e375.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200321%2Flarge%2F1584722812_e375.gif&h=8e48ca28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新澤西州一個大家庭月初聚餐，引發至少七名成員染疫。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n19名成員隔離檢測<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：專家倡立例要求商舖關門<br />\n<br />\n多人感染源頭應該來自月初一頓家庭飯敍；家人是在麗塔離世後，才知道她患有武漢肺炎。富斯科的表姊妹福德拉說，有19名家庭成員正在隔離，當中有「家中的孩子、父母與孫兒」，他們已於上周六進行了病毒檢測，但截至前天仍尚未收到結果，「他們皆因家人離世而感到焦慮不安，又不知道他們是否有感染」，「為何這些無住院的家庭成員未收到檢測結果？這是場公共衞生危機」。她又質疑「為何沒有症狀的運動員和名人都比被病毒破壞的家庭更優先」得到檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡/《紐約時報》"},{"pid":"e29ae6bb35bdd7508540dcb2a16cec01b47bb6fc","tid":1936211,"uid":18912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:47:28.000Z","msg":"ccpvirus"},{"pid":"820048af1f54cd29fc63c336e8497b0882eacd13","tid":1936211,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:47:51.000Z","msg":"just a flu 驚西<br />\n<br />\n無病洗撚戴罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃皮豬大驚少怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b06a94a60efd2cb025feffab34592e8fe5447cf","tid":1936211,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"反共未"},{"pid":"ab024ff6990912f2b7622039a501dde006f15e6f","tid":1936211,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚柒肥<br />\nJust a flu都危險喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed178f4c6a9ebb90138c9b600314f128b424d27","tid":1936211,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:53:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nytimes/status/1240463015071428609?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnytimes%2Fstatus%2F1240463015071428609%3Fs%3D21&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=3e856e3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnytimes%2Fstatus%2F1240463015071428609%3Fs%3D21&h=756e38ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nytimes/status/1240463015071428609?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n呢單新聞嘅NYTimes twitter link<br />\n麻煩大家加上 <span style=\"color: red;\">#ChineseVirus #ChinaLiesPeopleDie </span>之後retweet"},{"pid":"10210fc49a376048c4b32d0d80a60460ccc960fa","tid":1936211,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:57: